â— Why it matters
Staging archives in user-accessible locations (Documents/Downloads) is a strong indicator of intent to exfiltrate. Detecting archive creationâ€”especially when tied to scripting toolsâ€”can provide one of the last opportunities to contain the incident before data leaves the environment.
